[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]The proposal that providers of legal services in applications for judicial review against public bodies should only be paid for work done on the case if the Court grants permission
[normal] for the application to proceed – ‘judicial review’
[normal],
[normal] and
[normal]d)
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]The proposal that legal aid should be removed fo
[normal]r all cases assessed as having 
[normal]“
[normal]borderline
[normal]”
