[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]“Habeas corpus protection is often expressed as limited to British subjects. Is it really limited to British nationals? Suffice 
[normal]it to say that the case law has given an emphatic ‘no’ to the question. Every person within the jurisdiction enjoys the equal protection of our la
[normal]w
[normal]s.
[normal].
[normal].He who is subject to English law is entitled to its protection.” 
